data.description: Delightful brick ranch in the Westview subdivision. Situated in central Greeley, this charming home has much to offer. 4 beds, 2 baths, separate dining, southeast facing sun porch and finished basement. Furnace and AC units are 3 years old and newer roof as of 2018. Beautiful, original hardwood floors partially exposed and extend under carpeted areas on main level. New carpet in basement.
